climate, trend and extreme events analysis. Additionally, the data will
allow validating simulations of numerical atmospheric models. The
dataset is public, and it was previously used in other research to
determine areas susceptible to flooding due to heavy rain events and to
develop a web mapping application of daily precipitation data.},
